{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC01_WIL_720.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1b,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x169,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Starting with things we can still do from now... I wonder what I should do..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x16a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "To make Great-great-grandmother happy quickly, I need to do something big..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x16a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Even if I can't do it alone, it'll be possible with two people!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x16b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, let's work hard, and aim for something challenging!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Ehhh, let's not do something too challenging. We should do something we know we can do, and do it well..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "No, no, we'll be fine! I think it'll turn out fine somehow."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Y-You think...? So what's this challenging thing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm, I'm glad you asked. I actually have something in mind."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Since ancient times, witches have had three ultimate goals."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "One is to catch the wind, one is to eat a shadow..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "And one is to shatter the stars. I think Great-great-grandmother is the only person who can do all three."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Let's start with the one that sounds easiest, catching the wind."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Wind... Do you mean, like the ones that go whoosh, blowing all around?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Yup. We just need to catch the being that controls it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Catch the wind... I know this is gonna sound weird, but that's like grasping at smoke."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "The being that controls the wind...<CR>Is that like a wind spirit?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I think so, but even among spirits,<CR>we need to catch a super big one."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "There's no point in catching one that's nearby..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "So we need to subjugate a noble,<CR>top-class spirit!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Whattaya think? Doesn't that sound like something witchy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "It does, but do you think it'll be that easy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Besides, where are wind spirits anyways?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I know the place. It's in the skies beyond Hornheim!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I've seen one before over there."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Oh, now that you mention it, that does sound like a good place to start. But, isn't that a super wide area to look?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Well, that can't be helped."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "C'mon, let's go!"
        }
    ]
}